{"tid":1697980,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【老人院高登屠妖義士單手遊出公海高登仔】(30歲男子XX輝)疑兇無精神病紀錄 舊同學稱性情怪","createTime":"2019-11-07T07:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T08:14:37.000Z","uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"014b40a60f080f7722a5eb538b271479d29bea45","tid":1697980,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:54:52.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】立法會議員何君堯在屯門遇襲，疑兇為30歲姓董無業男子，根據網上搜尋結果，董的名字與一名活躍高登討論區的網民名字相同。有認識疑兇的人形容董自小性情古怪，沒有朋友，不清楚其行兇動機。據悉，董與父母及胞妹同住葵湧新葵芳花園，有街坊稱董日常行為怪異，曾見他自言自語玩手機。<br />\n<br />\n同名漢活躍高登 錄口供自稱「詩人」<br />\n涉嫌施襲30歲男子董X輝。據瞭解，董與家人居於葵青區，錄口供時自稱「詩人」，其父母向警方表示兒子沒有精神病紀錄。據知，董男為荃灣公立何傳耀紀念中學舊生，其舊同學形容董性情古怪，在校時較孤僻；她說多名校友昨日看到新聞圖片，才發現疑兇是舊同學，在校友群組內議論紛紛。<br />\n<br />\n記者翻查網上資料，發現一名活躍高登討論區動漫台、曾遭起底的網民的名字，與疑兇名字相同，外貌相似，但暫未能確認是否董。該網民有多個帳戶，其中一個以反修例運動命名的帳戶，但絕少發表與運動有關政見，反經常在動漫台與其他會員針鋒相對，故遭會員起底並張貼其容貌照。<br />\n<br />\n昨早疑現場附近商場買花<br />\n本報到案發現場附近的啟豐商場商戶查詢，獲商戶提供閉路電視片段，看到一名戴黑白色鴨舌帽、穿藍衫牛仔褲、背泥黃色袋、與施襲者打扮相似的男子，於昨早8時33分經過商場地下層，他當時正低頭用電話；至8時38分，該男子手持一束太陽花再經過，面露笑容，該花束與疑兇送給何君堯的花束類似。約8時44分，何君堯於啟豐商場門口遇襲。啟豐商場1樓的花店店主稱，花店昨晨8時開門，由丈夫看店，她不知道早上有何人買花束。"},{"pid":"bef4e7719c3c8db462201f49dd201c57d1eea345","tid":1697980,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:55:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-ort2-2.cdninstagram.com/vp/63c51d14223f4616c0cac680f1594e1e/5DD2153E/t51.2885-15/e35/s1080x1080/51325207_345739806281603_6164008730934409635_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-ort2-2.cdninstagram.com\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-ort2-2.cdninstagram.com%2Fvp%2F63c51d14223f4616c0cac680f1594e1e%2F5DD2153E%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2Fs1080x1080%2F51325207_345739806281603_6164008730934409635_n.jpg%3F_nc_ht%3Dscontent-ort2-2.cdninstagram.com&h=91417f3a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9cf2a01f5b832d30071df9e22a7d28f6d3234f0b","tid":1697980,"uid":42586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:56:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff7470b0c98fde985ae5a1b2bc6e5cb1e85b5b8","tid":1697980,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:57:04.000Z","msg":"兒登仔：收何妖錢自編自導自演<br />\n鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c27284e34135d3fed21285ca148ecd8111ff572","tid":1697980,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T08:14:37.000Z","msg":"不得不承認藍絲比我地團結太多<br />\n有廢老斬人 d藍絲實話斬得好<br />\n我地就第1時間諗係咪鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}